OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, a fine
OL,6,Fbut windy day is expected, and widely
OL,7,Fsunny. However, some high cloud will
OL,8,Flikely build and thicken from the
OL,9,Fnorthwest later. Feeling warm,
OL,10,Fespecially out the wind, but cooler in
OL,11,Fany onshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud will break at times,
OL,14,Fgiving some clearer spells and
OL,15,Fallowing for temperatures to fall.
OL,16,FWith winds easing, the odd patch of
OL,17,Ffrost and very isolated valley fog is
OL,18,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
