OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day.
OL,6,FWith lighter winds and lengthier sunny
OL,7,Fspells, it will be feeling warmer than
OL,8,Fon Tuesday for most.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FCooler Thursday, with showery
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain, clearing overnight
OL,13,Fwith frost possible. Likely staying
OL,14,Fdry Friday with variable cloud and
OL,15,Fsunny spells, but also windy. Further
OL,16,Frain spreading east Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
